languages.text: "Мои дикие гончие выйдут на арену вкусить крови отчаянных претендентов. Омывайте их страданиями свои души, делайте ставки, сможет ли кто-нибудь из них одолеть ловчих тварей!"
"My wild hounds will enter the arena to taste the blood of its wretched challengers. Bathe your souls in their suffering! Make your guesses at whether the prey can overpower the predators!"

languages.text: « Mes limiers vont entrer dans l'arène et faire couler le sang de leurs malheureux adversaires. Repaissez-vous de leurs souffrances ! Voyez si vous êtes prêts à parier sur la victoire de l'une des proies ! »

languages.text: “我的猎犬会进入竞技场，饱饮那些可怜挑战者的鲜血！让你们的灵魂尽情沐浴在他们的痛苦中吧！猜猜看，猎物究竟能否战胜捕猎者！”
languages.original_text: "My wild hounds will enter the arena to taste the blood of its wretched challengers. Bathe your souls in their suffering! Make your guesses at whether the prey can overpower the predators!"

languages.text: 「これから俺のどう猛な猟犬たちをアリーナに投入し、哀れな挑戦者どもの血を味わわせる。お前たちの魂を奴らの苦しみで満たせ！獲物が捕食者に勝てるかどうか、賭けてみるがいい！」
languages.original_text: "My wild hounds will enter the arena to taste the blood of its wretched challengers. Bathe your souls in their suffering! Make your guesses at whether the prey can overpower the predators!"

languages.text: "Meine wilden Hunde werden die Arena betreten, um das Blut der jämmerlichen Herausforderer zu kosten. Badet Eure Seelen in ihrem Leid! Was denkt Ihr – ob es die Beute schafft, die Räuber zu überwältigen?"
languages.original_text: "My wild hounds will enter the arena to taste the blood of its wretched challengers. Bathe your souls in their suffering! Make your guesses at whether the prey can overpower the predators!"

languages.text: «Mis perros salvajes saldrán a la arena para saborear la sangre de estos desdichados aspirantes. ¡Que su sufrimiento bañe vuestras almas! ¡Apostad por los depredadores o por sus presas!».

languages.text: "Vahşi tazılarım, kokuşmuş dövüşçülerin kanına doymak için arenaya girecek. Âcizlerin acısı, ruhunuzu beslesin! Avların, avcılara üstün gelip gelemeyeceği konusunda bahislerinizi oynayın!"
